snippet.title: Fight N' Fall Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Battle it out with 3 other friends in colorful fully destructive arenas. Select a character - or assemble your own - with a roster of unique and powerful spells. Last one standing wins!

We have been working hard on Fight N' Fall for the past 10 months and it's great being able to finally share it with you guys. Our plan is to keep posting as regular as we can and we will be starting a devlog series soon. So if you like the game make sure to subscribe here.

Wishlist Fight n' Fall on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1373890/Fight_N_Fall/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/fightnfall/


Release 2021
